"\n"
"sigc::signal&lt;void, bool, int&gt; signal_something;\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"sigc::signal&lt;void, bool, int&gt; signal_something;\n"

#: C/gtkmm-tutorial-in.xml:7779(para)
